graph LR
    RHODSOp[RHODS Operator<br/>v1.6.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    RHODSOp -->|requires| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    RHODSOp -->|requires| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.11+<br/>Routes, OAuth, Console]
    RHODSOp -->|built with| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.16.3]
    RHODSOp -->|uses| Kustomize[kustomize v0.13.4<br/>Manifest templating]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    RHODSOp -.->|optional| ServiceMesh[OpenShift Service Mesh 2.x<br/>Istio-based networking]
    RHODSOp -.->|optional| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.69.1<br/>Monitoring CRDs]
    RHODSOp -.->|optional| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Certificate provisioning]
    RHODSOp -.->|optional| Authorino[Authorino<br/>External authorization]

    %% Internal RHOAI Component Management
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Web UI, OdhDashboardConfig CR]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Jupyter, Notebook CRDs]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Kubeflow, DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| KServe[KServe<br/>Single-model serving, InferenceService CR]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Multi-model serving, ServingRuntime CR]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| CodeFlare[CodeFlare<br/>Distributed workloads, MCAD, InstaScale]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| Ray[Ray<br/>Distributed compute, RayCluster CR]
    RHODSOp -->|deploys/manages| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>Model monitoring, TrustyAIService CR]

    %% Platform Integration
    RHODSOp -->|creates| OAuthClients[OAuth Clients<br/>Component authentication]
    RHODSOp -->|creates| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>External access]
    RHODSOp -->|creates| NetworkPolicies[NetworkPolicies<br/>Network isolation]
    RHODSOp -->|creates| Monitoring[Monitoring Stack<br/>Prometheus, Alertmanager]

    %% Manifest Sources (Build-time)
    RHODSOp -->|embeds at build| Manifests["Component Manifests<br/>/opt/manifests/component/"]
    Manifests -.->|odh-dashboard repo| Dashboard
    Manifests -.->|notebooks repo| Workbenches
    Manifests -.->|dsp-operator repo| Pipelines
    Manifests -.->|kserve repo| KServe
    Manifests -.->|modelmesh repo| ModelMesh
    Manifests -.->|codeflare repo| CodeFlare
    Manifests -.->|kuberay repo| Ray
    Manifests -.->|trustyai repo| TrustyAI

    %% External Services
    RHODSOp -->|pulls from| Quay[quay.io<br/>Container images]
    RHODSOp -->|pulls from| RedHatRegistry[registry.redhat.io<br/>Red Hat images]
    RHODSOp -.->|dev mode| GitHub[github.com<br/>Manifest downloads]

